        E'End with numbered steps and follow requirement',
        ARRAY['white space between sections', 'checkmark emojis for lists', 'quotation marks for myths', 'numerals and ALL CAPS for CTAs', 'controversial opener', 'high-value deliverable promise', 'proof with pages/results', 'short numbered steps', 'myth-busting format', 'contrarian positioning', 'free template offer', 'social proof'],
        E'99% of people chase likes and stay broke.\n\nHere''s the $2M+ LinkedIn strategy that actually gets clients.\n\nYou''ve probably heard:\n\n"LinkedIn is oversaturated."\n"Just post daily and leads will come."\n"You need 10,000 followers before it works."\n\nNone of that is true.\nAnd it''s costing you clients.\n\nToday, I''m giving away the full system I use to close clients on LinkedIn — templates included.\n\nInside you''ll find:\n\n☑ DM scripts that convert strangers into leads\n☑ Content cadence framework that drives inbound\n☑ Profile funnel templates (optimized for discovery)\n☑ Calendar setup for automated booking\n☑ Step-by-step outreach system\n☑ 3 bonus case studies with numbers\n\n(It''s 105 pages of templates, screenshots, and examples.)\n\nLook no further:\nThis is the playbook I wish I had when I started.\n\nWant this?\n\n1. Comment BLUEPRINT below\n2. Follow me here\n3. I''ll DM it within 24 hours'
