        E'Our Internal AI Mega-Prompt Is Now Yours (For Free)\n\n(Built for us — now open for 48 hours)\n\nWe built this tool to automate what used to take 5 hours of manual work every day.\n\nIt''s our private AI prompt framework for systemizing research, writing, and ideation.\n\n✅ Generate 10+ ideas from one keyword\n✅ Auto-format long-form posts\n✅ Pull recent data points with context\n✅ Draft engaging hooks and CTAs instantly\n\nThe results?\nUsed internally for 3 months — saved 15+ hours/week and boosted output 3x.\n\nNo ChatGPT guesswork.\nNo repetitive prompt typing.\nNo flaky workflows.\n\nI''ve turned the entire tool + documentation into a downloadable package:\n→ Mega-prompt system\n→ Template builder\n→ Usage guide with examples\n→ Automation script (optional setup)\n\nThis is the exact system that powers our daily content machine — now yours, free for 48 hours.\n\nWant early access?\n\n1. Comment TOOLKIT below\n2. I''ll DM you the link\n\n(Only available until [date/time].)\n\nBONUS: Comment fast for lifetime updates.'
